title: 20 followers???
body:
That’s right my dudes this human being now has a whopping 20 FOLLOWERS!!! And that being said, I bet you’re wondering what I have in mind for this occasion. Well BUCKLE UP KIDDOS CUZ YA GIRL IS DOING REQUESTS!!! 

I will draw most things but it has to be sfw, nothing that’s rude to anbody, and not triggering. This is a safe environment here in my corner of the internet and I’m keeping it that way. ALSO! I’m not just in the Sanders Sides famdom so maybe expect different stuff too? 

Welp that’s all I have to say. I’m gonna put a whole bunch of fandoms in the tags so it spreads a bit. I’ll see y'all later! - Phi

blog.name: weirdandwackypokefusions
blog.title: Well that's strange!
blog.description:
Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary: Snimin, Sermin and Serprizion Snivy and Shaymin Land Form fusion, Servine and Shaymin Sky Form fusion and Serperior and Verizion...
caption:
Snimin, Sermin and Serprizion

Snivy and Shaymin Land Form fusion, Servine and Shaymin Sky Form fusion and Serperior and Verizion fusion

Snimin is Grass Type, Sermin is Grass/Flying Type, Serprizion is Grass/Fighting Type

Abilities: Snimin - Serene Grace, Sermin - Aerilate, Serprizion - Contrary

Snimin - The Bushy Back Pokemon, Sermin - The Confident Flyer Pokemon, Serprizion - The Justice Bringer Pokemon

Snimin is very timid and will use its bushy back to hide in the grass.  It is usually found sleeping in bushes.  It loves to eat berries.

Sermin - Sermin flies confidently through the sky and will judge others on their flying abilities.  It is sometimes seen racing other pokemon for pride. 

Serprizion - Serprizion feels a sense of justice and pride as it wanders through the forest.  It is only seen when disaster strikes. Its body moves like a snake in the air.

Request for @gamingfiker678. I hope you like them!
